{"tid":702881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[過河拆橋]特朗普批准對約500億美元中國商品加征關稅","createTime":"2018-06-15T09:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T13:04:19.000Z","uid":123264,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a1982f93aefcd28a6e37e4589459c3ab16b201","tid":702881,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"外電引述消息指，美國總統特朗普已批准對價值500億美元的中國商品加徵關稅，有關徵稅商品規模與4月份的提議一樣，但更瞄準中國科技領域產品。<br />\n<br />\n彭博引述5個不記名消息指，美國正準備公布一份完善的清單，專門針對中國希望佔據領先地位的科技領域。美國於4月時曾公布一份初步清單，目標是價值500億美元、約1,300種中國輸美產品。<br />\n<br />\n白宮曾表示，關稅在周五的清單發布後「不久」就將實施，不過日期還沒有敲定。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周三受訪時揚言，未來數周將就貿易問題，採取強硬態度與中國對峙。中國外交部發言人耿爽昨重申，若美方出台加徵關稅等貿易制裁，中美談判達成的所有經貿成果將不會生效。<br />\n<br />\n一早話撚完金仔就撚你中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90a21937e9fb016cac6bad3bf751d0af726af09","tid":702881,"uid":61280,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:28:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">music<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;My Friend........今天你如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？？&quot;</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c90b7347163cf2a8bd7f7c6f1e3cd01cd059ef3e","tid":702881,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"5000億--&gt;2000億--&gt;500億？"},{"pid":"c7645862ad50b5c58d20ed032cb753231616b645","tid":702881,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"無人格的毒男: 我有獨特的新聞技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454ec78d2b53d48b5a1b01bca9f253d8252f0c04","tid":702881,"uid":48139,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid"